reviewText: Changing all my gaither VHS tapes into DVDs that's a long task, but I love the music and I met th goodmans back the 70's and late 90's, been to 3 gaither concerts great music,which gaither would let the power fall instead of mark lowery jokes. You'll enjoy this DVD.
Very good video with great music
This DVD is from a few years ago and it was good to see all the old faces again. I just love the Gaither DVDs and can reccomend this one to all who like Gaither DVDs..Ray
This video is wonderful.  It came very soon after I ordered it, and it is in perfect condition.
